---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Section from "../components/ui/Section.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy • Face Fitness">
  <Section title="Privacy Policy">
    <div class="card">
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.6;">
        This Privacy Policy explains how this website (“Face Fitness”) handles personal data.
        If you have questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@example.com">hello@example.com</a>.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:18px;">Email list (Free guide & tips)</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.6;">
        If you sign up for the free mini-guide, we collect your email address (and optionally your name) to send you the guide
        and occasional tips related to face fitness. You can unsubscribe at any time using the unsubscribe link included in every email.
      </p>

      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.6;">
        We use MailerLite as our email service provider to store and manage subscribers and to send emails.
        MailerLite processes this information on our behalf as a service provider.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:18px;">Analytics (Google Analytics 4)</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.6;">
        We use Google Analytics 4 (GA4) to understand website traffic and improve the content and user experience.
        Analytics tracking is <strong>disabled by default</strong> and is only enabled after you provide consent via the cookie banner.
      </p>

      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.6;">
        When enabled, GA4 collects usage information such as pages visited, approximate location (country/region),
        device and browser information, and interaction events. We aim to use analytics in an aggregated way and
        do not use it to directly identify you.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:18px;">Cookies and consent</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.6;">
        We show a cookie banner where you can accept or reject analytics tracking.
        Your choice is stored locally in your browser (localStorage key: <code>cookie_consent_v1</code>).
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:18px;">How to withdraw consent</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.6;">
        You can withdraw consent at any time by clearing your browser storage for this website
        (delete localStorage entry <code>cookie_consent_v1</code>) and reloading the page. After that, the cookie banner
        will appear again and you can choose “Reject”.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:18px;">Third-party services</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.6;">
        Our course checkout and access are handled by an external course platform. If you click a checkout link,
        you will leave this website and their privacy policy will apply.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:18px;">Updates</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.6;">
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The latest version will always be published on this page.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
